<item>
 <title>Is College for Everyone?</title>
 <link>http://www.brown.edu/Departments/Political_Theory_Project/janus/events/lectures/is_college_for_everyone_0</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-type-datetime field-field-je-date&quot;&gt;
